# Web3Forms access key for the site feedback form.
# Public by design - safe to ship in client code.
# Get yours at https://app.web3forms.com/dashboard (create a form, copy the key).
#
# Local dev: copy this file to `.env` and fill in the value.
# Production (GitHub Pages): add a repository Actions secret named
# VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY with the same value. The deploy workflow
# (.github/workflows/deploy.yml) passes it to the build.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
